  "elapsed_s": 3.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] what he did, and that was the norm, how to live.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But for us, maybe these holes wasn't big enough to-- for a grown up person to hide, but it was a hiding place, and there was a hunt for children.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "One even heard sometimes that they were fighting for a place there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And this is just to speak about Plaszow and about when a manhunt-- hunt was going on.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Usually when somebody escapes, it was the norm of about 50 people being taken to the killing hill.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "That has another-- had another name too, but I've forgotten.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I think Austrian or [? maybe hill. ?] Anyway, and killed up there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And now before my-- the story, as I say, before the last story which I told you about when I was nearly killed by this commandant Goeth-- it was Goeth by the way, as my father look-- when he looked out the window, he saw him. there was an incident where off-- he was very proud of his-- of his workshop, the garage, because, because we know he was proud because everybody who was visiting him had to be shown to the garage.",
      "word_count": 83
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And, and one of these people working in the garage managed to tie himself on the lorry and anyway escaped.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "This person, by chance, I knew.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "I forgot his name now.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "In the book I call him Daniel because his name start with a D.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "But I met him after the war and learned about his escape, but that's not my story.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Anyway, he was-- he succeeded, one of the few.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "But then, of course, Goeth, Goeth, Goeth heard it, he ordered 50 to be killed.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
